        <p>We at Ede Men have <strong>researched</strong> and <strong>targeted</strong> multiple local Haitian NGOs that are known to be the most <strong>effective</strong> and <strong>impactful</strong> with their funding.<br>
        <br>Through Ede Men, you can view each NGO and make your contribution <strong>directly</strong> to them, at no cost to us!</p>
